Package com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.factory

Contains factory classes for creating item data, for use in commands that are issued to the i2 Analyze command service.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GradeFactory
    A factory for creating Grades to be used in calls to the command service
    IdentifierFactory
    A factory for creating ItemIdentifiers and identifier Strings to be used in calls to the command service.
    PropertyValueFactory
    A factory for creating PropertyValues to be used in calls to the command service.
    SecurityAccessPermissionFactory
    A factory for creating SecurityAccessPermissions to be used in calls to the command service.
    SecurityGrantPermissionFactory
    A factory for creating SecurityGrantPermissions to be used in calls to the command service.
    SourceInfoFactory
    A factory for creating SourceInfos to be used in calls to the command service.
